column5: Anyone stayed here? Is this drive to outpost very remote? How were the accommodations and the walleye fishing? Thanks for any help.
The output is boat to from the resort. Never stayed there. The lake is a big fish lake, not a numbers lake.
Buckeye, you're talking about Dogtooth Lake, right? I'm wondering about their outpost on Direct Lake.
Yes fished Dogtooth many times. We bring our own boats. The resort is right off the highway. You have to boat out to the outpost cabin.
Oh carp just looked at their website. Sorry. Yes I meant Dogtooth. Not familiar with Direct Lake.
